abstract: Being with people you love becomes more important than small digs and even arguing about Donald Trump.
snippet: Being with people you love becomes more important than small digs and even arguing about Donald Trump.
lead_paragraph: Anyone desperate enough to Google the term “holiday stress” will be rewarded (or become more overwhelmed) with about 395,000,000 results. Limit the search to “holiday stress statistics 2019” and the results come down to a measly 28,100,000 or so. There are even specific memes and GIFs on how to handle the financial, social and emotional stresses of the season, including my current favorite, the article that ran in this newspaper by a Buddhist teacher who advises practicing “acceptance,” an activity that even on nonholidays can often seem as challenging as climbing Mount Everest in an ice storm.

abstract: The president frequently injects his own words into statements he claims his supporters said on Fox News or elsewhere. They rarely publicly correct him.
snippet: The president frequently injects his own words into statements he claims his supporters said on Fox News or elsewhere. They rarely publicly correct him.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Watching Fox News ahead of Wednesday’s impeachment vote, President Trump gave a Twitter call out to one of his most combative allies in the House.

abstract: The economic impact of Boeing Co's planned halt of 737 MAX production will not be considered by U.S. regulators in their ongoing review of when to end the grounding of a plane involved in two major fatal crashes, U.S. Transportation Secretary Elaine Chao said on Friday.
snippet: The economic impact of Boeing Co's planned halt of 737 MAX production will not be considered by U.S. regulators in their ongoing review of when to end the grounding of a plane involved in two major fatal crashes, U.S. Transportation Secretary Elai...
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — The economic impact of Boeing Co's planned halt of 737 MAX production will not be considered by U.S. regulators in their ongoing review of when to end the grounding of a plane involved in two major fatal crashes, U.S. Transportation Secretary Elaine Chao said on Friday.
headline_main: U.S. Transport Chief Said Economic Issues Not a Factor in 737 MAX's Safety Review
headline_print_headline: U.S. Transport Chief Said Economic Issues Not a Factor in 737 MAX's Safety Review

abstract: The regulations will allow a wider group of investors to profit from the 2017 tax provision that was pitched as a boon to low-income areas.
snippet: The regulations will allow a wider group of investors to profit from the 2017 tax provision that was pitched as a boon to low-income areas.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — The Trump administration finished regulations this week that will make it easier for wealthy Americans to invest in and benefit from opportunity zones, a tax incentive created in 2017 that was intended to funnel investment into low-income communities.

abstract: Why and how the young rule our time.
snippet: Why and how the young rule our time.
lead_paragraph: There are eras in history, like the 1950s, when older people set the cultural and moral terms for the young. And there are eras, like the 1960s, when it’s the other way around.

abstract: Brazilian President Jair Bolsonaro said on Friday that U.S. President Donald Trump told him in a phone conversation that his administration will not levy new tariffs on Brazilian steel and aluminium as threatened earlier this month.
snippet: Brazilian President Jair Bolsonaro said on Friday that U.S. President Donald Trump told him in a phone conversation that his administration will not levy new tariffs on Brazilian steel and aluminium as threatened earlier this month.
lead_paragraph: SAO PAULO — Brazilian President Jair Bolsonaro said on Friday that U.S. President Donald Trump told him in a phone conversation that his administration will not levy new tariffs on Brazilian steel and aluminium as threatened earlier this month.
headline_main: U.S. Won't Levy Threatened Tariffs on Brazil Steel, Trump Told Bolsonaro
headline_print_headline: U.S. Won't Levy Threatened Tariffs on Brazil Steel, Trump Told Bolsonaro

abstract: The magazine founded by the late Reverend Billy Graham that is influential with conservative evangelical Christians in the United States called on Thursday for President Donald Trump to be removed from office.
snippet: The magazine founded by the late Reverend Billy Graham that is influential with conservative evangelical Christians in the United States called on Thursday for President Donald Trump to be removed from office.
lead_paragraph: (Reuters) - The magazine founded by the late Reverend Billy Graham that is influential with conservative evangelical Christians in the United States called on Thursday for President Donald Trump to be removed from office.
headline_main: Billy Graham's Evangelical Magazine Calls for Trump's Removal
headline_print_headline: Billy Graham's Evangelical Magazine Calls for Trump's Removal

abstract: The Illinois Republican Party is ramping up efforts to make voters aware that an anti-Semitic activist and Holocaust denier who won the GOP nomination two years ago is again a candidate for the U.S. Congress, officials said.
snippet: The Illinois Republican Party is ramping up efforts to make voters aware that an anti-Semitic activist and Holocaust denier who won the GOP nomination two years ago is again a candidate for the U.S. Congress, officials said.
lead_paragraph: CHICAGO — The Illinois Republican Party is ramping up efforts to make voters aware that an anti-Semitic activist and Holocaust denier who won the GOP nomination two years ago is again a candidate for the U.S. Congress, officials said.
headline_main: Illinois GOP Aims to End Holocaust Denier's Run for Congress
headline_print_headline: Illinois GOP Aims to End Holocaust Denier's Run for Congress
